{"article_id":"tixjJ8PzYvksWril","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Arizona Sen. Jeff Flake is leaving Congress","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"because the kind of conservatism","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"he champions","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"no longer seems welcome in Steve Bannon 's GOP .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Flake , one of the few senators","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"willing to speak up against President Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"said Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"he would not seek re-election .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"He was facing a tough primary challenge from Kelli Ward , a populist","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"who already had secured the backing of Bannon , Trump 's former chief strategist .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"\" It is clear at this moment that a traditional conservative","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"who believes in limited government and free markets ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"who is devoted to free trade ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"who is pro-immigration","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"has a narrower and narrower path to nomination in the Republican Party , \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Flake said on the Senate floor Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"in announcing","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"he would not be seeking another term .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Later , Flake said to reporters ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"\" if I could run the kind of race","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"I 'd like to run","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"and believe","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"I could win a Republican primary ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"I might go forward . \"","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Before being elected to the Senate in 2012 ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Flake had served six terms in the House ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"where he built a reputation as a crusader against wasteful government spending .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"He built a reliable conservative voting record","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"- the American Conservative Union gave him a 93 % lifetime rating -","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"but his criticism of the president had alienated many of Arizona ' s far-right voters , the very voters most likely to show up for midterm primaries .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Trump was not timid in punching back at Flake ,","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"saying over the summer","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"that he was `` weak on borders '' and `` toxic . ''","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Flake became a key target of Bannon and his band of anti-establishment allies ,","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"who have vowed to put up candidates against any senator","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"- in either party -","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"who was hampering Trump ' s agenda","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"or was too close to Majority Leader Mitch McConnell of Kentucky .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Bannon ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"who was a senior adviser to Trump until this summer","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"when he returned to his post as the head of Breitbart News ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"even flew down to Arizona for a campaign rally for Ward last week .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"\" Today Steve Bannon and the entire Trump movement added another scalp to his collection","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"and other Never Trump incumbents should be very nervous right now , \"","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Andrew Surabian , a senior adviser for the pro-Trump advocacy organization Great America Alliance and a close ally of Bannon ' s , told shortly after the announcement .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"\" Arizona voters are the big winner in @ JeffFlake 's decision","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"to not seek reelection .","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"They deserve a strong , conservative in the Senate , \"","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Ward tweeted after the announcement .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"\" Who supports @ POTUS & the 'America First ' agenda .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Our campaign proudly offers an optimistic path forward for Arizona & America # MAGA \"","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"she continued .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Flake says","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"he will not seek re-election in 2018 ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"citing nastiness of Trump-era politics","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Jeff Flake threw out some zingers during his Senate floor speech","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"criticizing Trump","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Read Flake 's bombshell Senate speech :","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"'Mr . President , I rise today","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"to say :","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Enough '","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Why Sen. Jeff Flake says","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"he wo n't run for re-election to the Senate","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"Danny Tarkanian , the anti-establishment Republican","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"whom Bannon has indicated support for","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"and who is running against GOP Sen. Dean Heller in Nevada ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"was invigorated by the news .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"\" It will be interesting to see","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"whether Heller decides to follow the Corker-Flake model or the Luther Strange model .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"Either way he will not be the Republican nominee , \"","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Tarkanian told .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Strange is a sitting senator from Alabama","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"who was endorsed by GOP leadership and Trump","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"but was defeated last month in the GOP primary by Judge Roy Moore , a controversial candidate","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"endorsed by Bannon .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"When Flake was asked by reporters what his response was to the Bannon wing","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"claiming victory after his announcement ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"he responded :","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"`` Nothing at all . ''","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Tennessee Sen. Bob Corker , another lawmaker","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"who is retiring at the end of his term","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"and has battled with Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Flake `` is kind of quiet","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"but he stands for all the things","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"that have made our nation great","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"and he ' s willing to continue to say that","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"even though we have demagogues and others","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"who end up trying to take us in other directions . \"","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"Flake 's departure may just be a signal","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"that some people can not compete in the new Republican political climate .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"\" Most incumbents are realizing","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"that the old ways","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"of doing things ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"aren ' t going to work anymore .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"The old ways","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"of raising money","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"and doing TV ads","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"isn ' t going to work , \"","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"said Adam Brandon , president of the conservative advocacy group FreedomWorks .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"Brandon said","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"while Flake ' s voting record had always been good with FreedomWorks ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"he thought","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"the Arizona senator was \" too close to the swamp . \"","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":211,"left":0,"right":210,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":210,"left":129,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":109,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":1,"right":108,"relation":"causal","nuclearit